How did you know
about the possibility

00:33:00.200 --> 00:33:05.210 align:middle line:84%
of social media, its importance,
fake news, censorship?

00:33:05.210 --> 00:33:06.650 align:middle line:90%
How did you pick that up?

00:33:06.650 --> 00:33:08.870 align:middle line:90%
You were way ahead of yourself.

